/**
 * Comma-Separated Value Grammar
 * ECMA-404 The JSON Data Interchange Standard.
 *
 * Reference: 
 *  RFC4180 http://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc4180
 *
 * Authors:
 *  K. Kuramitsu 
